comment:
this is just my take on the whole thing. fuck cancel culture in all forms. yes this is a form of  cancel culture. people are people no one is perfect. every one of us has people who love us and people who hate us. if each one of us had our personal lives put under the microscope of the "press" do you think everyone would condone each and every actin you do? no they wouldn't every one would be drug through the mud and some might even deserve it. in this case let the court of law sort it out not the court of public opinion. 
i see a lot of comments saying " i wont watch this because of her". that's like everybody causing a business to be shut down because of one employee's personal life that has not one thing to do with how they perform at work. so just because that one person you want everyone to suffer and lose money. imagine this, you are going through a divorce or break up and then you get fired because of it. how about this example you work the drive through at big business burgers, you are great at your job. you have made employee of the month 3 times in a row. now you lose your job because some one said blah blah blah. it gets in the local news goes viral every one boycotts the place you worked it goes under thousands of people lose their jobs. to beat it all when the incident happened you weren't even working for that place yet. 
smh. piss on this social credit shit. piss on all this sjw shit. piss on cancel culture. piss on communism and socialism. piss on those reporters who only seek the next big headline regardless of the truth. wait for the whole story to come out. dont let one individual's actions spoil something you might enjoy. for example,  zuckerfuck is a dillweed piece of shit in a lot of peoples eyes. a lot of people dont like him but they still have Facebook accounts. why? because Facebook is a pretty good product. ray kroc was a bit of a shit stain and done the McDonald's brothers kind of dirty but we made that bastard billions. why? because we enjoyed the product. gordon ramsay is an asshole but people still want to eat his food. why? because he is good at his job, even though he is a dick head. 
how many people still have r. kelly on their play list? 
hell i could go on and on but the point i'm trying to make is if the movie is good enjoy it. if not flame the ever loving hell out of it. just dont let one person who is portraying a fictional character ruin something hundreds of other people have put a lot of work into. btw i'm not defending any one in this. i'm defending what i hope will be a entertaining movie. 
peace and love to all. 
end of rant.
